These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, march, january, september
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, tennis, golf, rowing
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, horse, rabbit
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, fishing, traveling, woodworking
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 7. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
10. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's birthday is in may##7
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
13. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Birthday   | september    | march | january    | may   |
| Sport   | weightlifting | golf | tennis | rowing |
| Pet           | dog       | horse   | rabbit  | cat     |
| Hobby     | gardening      | traveling   | woodworking    | fishing    |

