.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
House: townhouse, cape-cod, victorian, gothic-revival
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, thriller, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hedgehog, ferret, rabbit
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, iris, daffodil, poppy
 1. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
 2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
 3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the gothic-revival house##5
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
 7. the gothic-revival house is somewhere between the person who growsiris and the owner of the chinchilla##7
 8. the townhouse house is in an odd position##4
 9. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
10. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person who growstulip##5
11. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| House          | townhouse   | victorian       | gothic-revival    | cape-cod      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | time-travel | crime         | thriller   |
| Pet   | rabbit   | chinchilla  | hedgehog       | ferret |
| Flower         | tulip      | daffodil  | poppy | iris |

