The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, funk, metal, reggae
There are 4 different nationalities: german, polish, russian, spanish
House: gothic-revival, modern, farmhouse, victorian
 1. the victorian house is somewhere to the left of the fan of metal##5
 2. the victorian house is somewhere between the alhambra-smoker and the fan of metal##7
 3. the fonseca-smoker is the polish##1
 4. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
 5. the german is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 6. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the right of the fan of disco##5
 7. the game-smoker is not the fan of funk##6
 8. the fan of metal is not the blend-smoker##6
 9. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
10. the victorian house is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
11. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
12. the russian is the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Cigar           | blend | alhambra | fonseca | game |
| Music-Genre   | disco        | reggae    | funk    | metal    |
| Nationality   | german        | spanish   | polish   | russian         |
| House           | modern          | gothic-revival       | victorian   | farmhouse           |

