.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, february, october, september
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, lilac, orange, green
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, trike, subway, snowmobile
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, satire
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 5. the person who likes black is not the person watching crime movies##6
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 7. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person who likes lilac and the person who likes black##7
 9. the person driving the trike is the person watching crime movies##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
11. the person driving the bus is not the person watching crime movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |        3        |      4       |
| Birthday      | december | october       | february         | september       |
| Color         | black     | green    | orange   | lilac |
| Transport           | snowmobile   | trike | subway | bus     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire      | crime          | drama           | martial-arts |

