10. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
11. the turkish is the coach##1
12. the accountant is somewhere between the coach and the fan of r&b##7
13. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the brazilian##3

.:: Answer ::.
