.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, soy-milk, tea
4 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, bridge, whist
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, light-blue, red, green
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, april, june, september
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is not the person drinking coffee##6
 2. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
 3. the person who likes azure is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 7. the person who likes red is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking almond-milk##7
 8. the person who likes light-blue is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
10. the person who likes azure is the person who's birthday is in april##1
11. the person playing billiard is between the person playing whist and the person who likes light-blue##2
12. the person who likes green is the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea       | coffee     | soy-milk | almond-milk |
| Game          | bridge | monopoly     | billiard | whist     |
| Color           | green | light-blue | red    | azure      |
| Birthday   | august | september  | june | april     |

