 1. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person watching horror movies and the person watching zombie movies##7
 2. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person drinking water##7
 3. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 4. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
 5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
 6. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 7. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
 8. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person traveling to hamburg and the person traveling to venice##7
10. the person watching zombie movies is in an even position##4
11. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
12. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
13. the person watching animation movies is not the owner of the goat##6
14. the person watching horror movies is not the person traveling to hannover##6
15. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the person traveling to paris##7

.:: Answer ::.
