 8. the owner of the snake is not the fan of electronic##6
 9. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
10. the person driving the car is on the left of the french##1
11. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
12. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Pet         | rabbit      | turtle   | snake   | ferret       |
| Transport   | scooter | car    | ship | taxi       |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | colombian | french   | malaysian     |
| Music-Genre         | electronic   | disco    | punk   | country |

