.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, japanese, nigerian, polish
There 4 different types of food: apricot, artichoke, lemon, pear
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, orchid, balloon-flower, marigold
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, paramedic, project-manager, police-officer
 1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the nigerian##1
 2. the police-officer is somewhere to the left of the person eating apricot##5
 3. the person who growsmarigold is between the police-officer and the project-manager##2
 4. the person who growslily is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is not the paramedic##6
 6. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the left of the person eating lemon##5
 7. the polish is somewhere between the australian and the person eating pear##7
 8. the polish is somewhere to the left of the project-manager##5
 9. the freelancer is somewhere to the left of the person who growsorchid##5
10. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
11. the australian is the person eating lemon##1
12. the person eating lemon is not the project-manager##6

.:: Answer ::.
