.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, british, turkish
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, amber, azure, apricot
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, designer, police-officer, writer
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, bike, airplane, train
 1. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the british##5
 2. the person driving the helicopter is between the person who likes azure and the architect##2
 3. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the turkish##3
 4. the british is on the far right##1
 5. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person driving the bike is not the police-officer##6
 7. the police-officer is somewhere between the person who likes apricot and the person who likes turquise##7
 8. the person driving the helicopter is not the person who likes turquise##6
 9. the writer is not the person who likes apricot##6
10. the chinese is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
11. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person driving the train##1
12. the person who likes azure is not the chinese##6
13. the police-officer is on the left of the writer##1
14. the architect is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
15. the designer is on the left or right of the turkish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Nationality      | chinese      | brazilian        | turkish          | british    |
| Color         | apricot | amber    | azure          | turquise |
| Job           | architect  | designer   | police-officer | writer      |
| Transport   | train       | helicopter | airplane          | bike        |

