.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, documentary, mystery, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, metal, indie, disco
4 different games are played: go, whist, backgammon, monopoly
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rowing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 2. the fan of indie is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is the person playing monopoly##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching documentary movies##2
 5. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5
 6. the person playing go is somewhere between the fan of indie and the person watching drama movies##7
 7. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the fan of metal##5
 8. the person playing go is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the fan of pop##5
10. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
12. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire      | mystery     | documentary   | drama    |
| Music-Genre     | disco | indie   | metal | pop |
| Game     | monopoly        | backgammon     | go  | whist      |
| Sport   | rowing       | water-polo | cricket   | skiing    |

 